name: The Original Little Black Brooch - Aqua Boy Turquoise
description:
This Original Little Black Brooch features a beautifully modern black cameo set on a rich turquoise 'mirrored' oval, mounted on a black ornate frame, and surrounded by Blue Zircon Swarovski Crystals, all of which have been glued on by hand. 

This exclusive brooch design introduces a modern twist to the classic elements of the traditional cameo by using sturdy, laser-cut perspex, resulting in a strong and clearly defined, architectonic piece of vintage-inspired jewellery. 

Designed, cut and hand-assembled in Australia. 

This brooch measures
48mm x 60mm -outside frame
28mm x 38mm -inside oval
25mm x 16mm -cameo
and 10mm deep
set on a
20mm silver plated disc, with safety catch on pin

name: LBB Cameo Chain Bracelet
description:
This LBB Cameo Chain Bracelet features our beautifully modern cameo cut into  five perspex ovals, all linked together with sturdy brass rings to make this bold cameo chain. It has been designed with an extra linkage of chain which is finished with a coloured drop crystal, and also features our LBB makers mark.

...Please note, this bracelet comes in both black and cream...

This exclusive bracelet design introduces a modern twist to the classic elements of the traditional cameo by using sturdy, laser-cut perspex, resulting in a strong and clearly defined, architectonic piece of vintage-inspired jewellery. 

Designed, cut and hand-assembled in Australia. 

This bracelet measures 210mm in length, with an extra 35mm chain for extra linkage if necessary. This chain also has the dual purpose of using it to fasten the bracelet single handed, please see bottom photo for an example.

name: LBB Cameo Candy Stud Earrings
description:
These cute little laser-cut cameo earrings are designed exclusively for LBB and set on allergen-free surgical steel earposts. The cameos measure approximately 7.5mm wide and 12mm long,  and are cut from a sturdy perspex.

available in a variety of candy colours, see the drop down menu below.

name: The Original LBB Cameo Pendant
description:
This stunning piece is EXCLUSIVE to our new LBB 'cameo collection'. Celebrating the classic cameo whilst giving it a modern twist...

This vintage-fusion pendant features our signature cameo silhouette, designed by Vanessa Kellas and laser cut with modern precision which then hangs from a vintage watch fob clasp aged to a deep patina. It is completed with a vintage metal chain tassel, that is made from copper washed steel and brass, and have added our customised LBB brass makers mark for authenticity. The simple brass chain measures 30inches, but the 'total' hanging length of this piece including the tassel is 22inches, which sits lower chest.  

This pendant is available in black or cream. 

Please note, due to the vintage nature of some of these beautiful findings, a small amount of tarnish on some of the pieces are to be expected, a testament to their fine age and memories...

You are also able to buy multiples of the same design. Please use the reference code to the right for your selection. 

All cards are exclusively designed by Vanessa Kellas for LBB, printed locally in Byron Bay on 100% recycled card, 10.5mm x 14.75mm and come with a coloured c6 envelope and clear sleeve to protect the artwork. They are left blank inside for your own personal message.

name: LBB Luxury Custom Fabric Purses (with free candy earrings)
description:
This debut range of designer fabric features 'Velma the Crow' in all her cameo glory.  Exclusively designed by Vanessa Kellas for LBB using eco-friendly, water-based pigment inks on natural fiber textiles and is available in 4 glorious colour ways. Please select from the drop down menu below.

(This product comes with a gift of LBB cameo candy earrings valued at rrp.$15.00, which will be randomly selected for you, unless you specify in the notes which colour you prefer.)

These purses measure a very handy 6 x 8 inches, perfect for using as a make-up pouch or simply as a purse for your phone and keys, and they are fully lined with a classic pinstripe design. To finish, a luxurious tassel turns this purse into something just that extra bit special...

Care instructions - Please remove tassel before washing. This linen/cotton blend requires gentle hand or a delicate machine wash, using phosphate free detergent. Air dry only and lightly iron to finish. 

This product is designed and sewn in Byron Bay.

name: To catch a falling Rockstar Earrings
description:

Catch a falling rockstar, close your eyes and make a wish...
